{"tid":2260321,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"美國發生大火：即將燒至共雪總部員工現已撤離","createTime":"2020-10-27T13:14:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-27T17:41:36.000Z","uid":33359,"like":152,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"78f51735619a54baaef7fc4403ac0413377bebcb","tid":2260321,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T13:14:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.xfastest.com/blizzard/86957/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%99%BC%E7%94%9F%E5%A4%A7%E7%81%AB%EF%BC%9A%E5%8D%B3%E5%B0%87%E7%87%92%E8%87%B3%E6%9A%B4%E9%9B%AA%E7%B8%BD%E9%83%A8%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E7%8F%BE%E5%B7%B2%E6%92%A4%E9%9B%A2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.xfastest.com%2Fblizzard%2F86957%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%2599%25BC%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%2581%25AB%25EF%25BC%259A%25E5%258D%25B3%25E5%25B0%2587%25E7%2587%2592%25E8%2587%25B3%25E6%259A%25B4%25E9%259B%25AA%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E9%2583%25A8%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E7%258F%25BE%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E6%2592%25A4%25E9%259B%25A2%2F&d=BCqMRPjRs%2BrlYbPtDS4RDARqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=7fe5cced\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.xfastest.com/blizzard/86957/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%99%BC%E7%94%9F%E5%A4%A7%E7%81%AB%EF%BC%9A%E5%8D%B3%E5%B0%87%E7%87%92%E8%87%B3%E6%9A%B4%E9%9B%AA%E7%B8%BD%E9%83%A8%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E7%8F%BE%E5%B7%B2%E6%92%A4%E9%9B%A2/</a><br />\n<br />\n如果《魔獸世界：暗影國度》沒有延期上線時間，那麼今天魔獸玩家們就已經在體驗新版本了。<br />\n<br />\n但暴雪面臨了一個更大的危機，美國加州Silverado Canyon的大火現在已經蔓延至了暴雪總部的附近，這場大火已經吞沒了7200英畝的土地，目前已有超過90000萬名居民進行了撤離。<br />\n<br />\n暴雪總部目前雖然還不在撤離區域內，但他們的員工已經進行了撤離。<br />\n<br />\n巧合的是由於新冠疫情的持續，暴雪的大多數員工都在家辦公，所以暴雪總部內並沒有多少員工。目前大火距離暴雪總部還有8公里左右的距離，現場已有500多名消防員，其中有兩位身受重傷正在接受治療。<br />\n<br />\n暗黑社區負責人表示他們今日在暴雪總部進行了火災預警，圖中黑色方框就是暴雪總部所在地。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，暴雪總部員工表示他們已經撤離。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.xfastest.com/data/attachment/forum/202010/27/170936ml0b0vtk0ebe6end.jpg.thumb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.xfastest.com%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fforum%2F202010%2F27%2F170936ml0b0vtk0ebe6end.jpg.thumb.jpg&h=4e15b2e7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4664164bd895fdcbc9c0fd5bbd14749de189b1ba","tid":2260321,"uid":132326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T13:14:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2c53b60c262cefa2be049910deb4b1d46f00210","tid":2260321,"uid":318712,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T13:15:07.000Z","msg":"時事師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f9a8954cba42f5d15279bace9c18bac6fc76df3","tid":2260321,"uid":295230,"like":58,"dislike":0,"score":58,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T13:15:27.000Z","msg":"90000萬名居民<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2e078f3bf1340679ae4750cf53d1725009a3efe","tid":2260321,"uid":211578,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T13:15:28.000Z","msg":"大火師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ed2a14b846eaf136b16c5b5381a5e43cc6fa818","tid":2260321,"uid":128741,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T13:15:39.000Z","msg":"共雪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bca00b3e43fca7c44baeb8e5f9f60e879900447","tid":2260321,"uid":128741,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"5f9a8954cba42f5d15279bace9c18bac6fc76df3","tid":2260321,"uid":295230,"like":58,"dislike":0,"score":58,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T13:15:27.000Z","msg":"90000萬名居民<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/